MDXVII.

ASSIGNMENT BY THOMAS OARDIFFE, OF BETTUS, AND HIS WIFE ANN, OF A LEASE OF LAND OALLED GWAYNE DAVID TEWE, IN THE LORDSHIP OF OOURT OOLE- MAN, TO EDWARD FROWD, OF TYTHEGSTOWE.

[MARGAM CHARTER] 21 M 1654 AY. .
